Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.47,0:00:15.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to shine on you,\Nand always like that dazzling sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.38,0:00:18.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I will defend you\Nfrom all the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:24.75,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:39.54,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If only our hearts could connect,\NI could get you to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.64,0:00:46.31,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you can't\Nsee it now, don't lose it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.48,0:00:54.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your kindness won't be in vain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:01:01.66,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be carried aloft by the wind\Nto somewhere that isn't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:08.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You'll cross the sea and cross time,\Nand I know you'll blossom one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:15.41,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the day,\NI'll be there for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.84,0:01:22.05,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope I can watch over you\Nlike the sun for all time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:32.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the truth from my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:39.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! This will accomplish nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.74,0:01:58.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me! Put away\Nyour spears and return to Kanball
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.82,0:02:01.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you intend to\Ncontinue such a futile endeavor?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.66,0:02:12.66,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 22\NSeason of Awakening
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.87,0:02:51.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.44,0:03:34.24,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At that point, it had nothing to do\Nwith the King's Spears or anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:38.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a battle to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.49,0:03:50.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that was how Jiguro\Nkilled all of the King's Spears...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:52.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...who had been\Nsent to hunt us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:56.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He did it to protect\Nboth me and himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:04:03.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But in the process, his own soul was\Nlost along with those eight people's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Along with the eight people's?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:11.75,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right. The souls I talked about the\Nnight I took you under my protection...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.75,0:04:14.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...were those of the\NKing's Spears that Jiguro killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.09,0:04:21.79,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because of Logsam, Jiguro and I\Nwere forced to walk a cruel path in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:30.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, those dead men didn't\Ndeserve to be killed over nothing either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.57,0:04:36.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you see, my life has been\Nbuilt on their sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:45.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Care to eat dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.12,0:04:51.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you swore to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:56.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...save the same number of\Npeople that Jiguro killed, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:05:01.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Jiguro told me to\Nforget about it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.43,0:05:05.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But if it weren't for that vow,\NI would be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:10.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that was\Nmy reason for doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:13.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But aside from the fact\Nthat my father was his friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...Jiguro had no reason to save me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:22.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why was Jiguro willing to kill\Neight of his friends to save you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:28.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. That question\Nhas always bothered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.39,0:05:30.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he agree to\Nmy father's request?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.23,0:05:34.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't he abandon me\Nsomewhere along the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:40.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did he agree to something\Nthat would gain him nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.14,0:05:43.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and would cost him everything\Nthat he had worked for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:49.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to find out why he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.45,0:05:55.99,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I could understand\Nwhat Jiguro was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.69,0:06:01.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...maybe I could accept my\Nown situation a little better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:08.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Care to continue the discussion\Nover dinner downstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like reminiscing\Nabout Jiguro too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:32.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After the fight with the King's Spears\Nwas over, what did you do, Balsa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:38.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My training with Jiguro\Nwas complete by that point...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:43.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...so my skills were more than a\Nmatch for any of the local warriors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I was 16 by then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:50.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...so I understood\NJiguro's suffering all too well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:52.48,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I said to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.91,0:06:56.61,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Let's go our separate ways."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:19.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jiguro, let's split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:24.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can take care of myself now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.78,0:07:33.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:38.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've already saved\Nme so many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:41.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So please, forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.39,0:07:46.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on your own\Nhappiness from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.98,0:08:03.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You may feel as if you\Nowe me an enormous debt...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...but don't think of\Nthe past that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only leave you\Nwith an empty feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:13.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Balsa...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:17.66,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've grown fond of\Nboth you and our life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.76,0:08:24.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When Jiguro said that,\NI was at a loss for words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.13,0:08:28.17,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But in spite of what he said...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:32.34,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...he had tried his utmost\Nto avoid fighting his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:36.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And even though he said\Nhe was fond of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:39.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that certainly wasn't\Nthe case at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:41.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, women may have...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:45.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...maternal instincts, but they aren't\Nsomething men are born with.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:52.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I never learned\Nwhat Jiguro was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.46,0:08:54.76,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...when he first escaped with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:09:01.27,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Some five years\Nafter that, Jiguro died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:07.98,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't defeated by pursuers.\NHe succumbed to an illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:11.85,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By that time,\NKing Logsam was dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:16.62,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...so there was no reason\Nfor us to keep living like fugitives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:21.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen years had passed\Nsince the two of us first left Kanbal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.46,0:09:29.47,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I give you my word.\NI'll save eight souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:32.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lay your friends'\Nsouls to rest. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So please...rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.81,0:09:39.94,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:45.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's much harder to save lives\Nthan it is to take them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:49.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to become\Na hero or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:55.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,People often yearn for a hero\Nwho will sacrifice his life for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:10:00.46,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saving lives isn't something\Nthat you do on a whim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:03.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop trying so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.30,0:10:11.41,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, Chagum,\Nthis is how I see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.01,0:10:19.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Jiguro was someone who\Nthought if you're in a position to act...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.65,0:10:24.89,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...it would be a sin not to, even if you\Nhad nothing to gain from doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:31.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Jiguro, being a national hero and\Nprotecting some nameless person...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:33.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...they were the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:38.77,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He even hoped to spare the\Nlives of his pursuers if he could.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:45.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.74,0:10:49.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After becoming your bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:07.00,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moribito Guardian of the Spirit
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:10.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't talk you out of going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.03,0:11:12.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time like the present.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.37,0:11:16.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, winter will be at its\Nharshest over the next two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.01,0:11:20.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't leave now, the snow\Nwill have me good and stuck here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:24.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have better things to do than spend\Nthe whole winter cooped up in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:27.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Surely you don't need to\Ngo to the health springs...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:29.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...at an important time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:33.42,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, I'll be back\Nbefore the spring thaw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:37.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mistress Torogai,\Nare you going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:39.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To the hot springs, boy!\NThe hot springs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:40.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:44.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum, why are\Nyou carrying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:47.64,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Teach me how to fight too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:53.18,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to learn as much as I can\Nto protect the egg and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.51,0:11:59.15,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm stronger, I might be able to\Nget away even if Rarunga attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:04.69,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and I might be able to make sure\Nthe egg hatches safely even if I die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:08.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm the\Nguardian of the spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.27,0:12:21.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.44,0:12:27.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not going to let you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:29.81,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:38.82,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Teacher...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:40.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.32,0:12:43.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was unusual, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.63,0:12:45.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, you can make\Nthat expression too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.63,0:12:47.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one cares what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.86,0:12:48.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.70,0:12:54.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa, feel free to train the boy\Nif you want, but don't go overboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:13:00.74,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, he doesn't seem to\Nhave any talent for the martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.74,0:13:02.31,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.31,0:13:04.78,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph, I'm just stating the facts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.78,0:13:06.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.22,0:13:18.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Caw, caw, hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:24.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will tomorrow bring fair\Nweather, a blizzard, or rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.70,0:13:30.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the Misty Blues\Nare slightly cloudy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:36.71,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let the paddies dry out.\NCall for water!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.71,0:13:43.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nurture the seedlings\Nand spread the fertilizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.35,0:13:49.63,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nahji, fly, fly! Nahji, fly, fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.63,0:13:58.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you fly to the sea,\Nthe rice plants will grow swiftly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:04.57,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, why are you\Nstanding there in the doorway?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:07.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.74,0:15:13.11,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking that\Nthis really takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.84,0:15:17.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jiguro sometimes watched\Nover you as you slept...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:20.22,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...after the day's training was over,\Njust like you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:53.88,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa, this winter has\Nbeen a good one, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.68,0:15:57.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With the three of us\Ntogether like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:16:00.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I hoped that this winter\Nwould go on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:03.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But spring will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.53,0:16:05.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,These quiet days are almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:09.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rarunga will probably\Nbe waking soon too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:13.70,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably. We'll be facing\Na life-or-death struggle soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:25.45,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa, if we all make it\Nthrough this battle alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:28.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...how about the three of us\Nliving together like we did this winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:35.92,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been\Nhesitant to bring it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.43,0:16:39.86,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I should wait until\Nafter you'd fulfilled your promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.43,0:16:44.30,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I did wait,\Nyou'd never notice it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Battles are your whole\Nlife now, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:04.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure how I can cure that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.62,0:17:07.29,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any medicine for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:17.67,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't think of me as the cure,\NI guess there's no point in me waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:34.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:38.05,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think I have\Nenough on my mind right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.55,0:18:37.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:40.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter? Chagum!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:48.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum, what in the\Nworld happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.96,0:18:53.13,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:19:00.00,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no ground...\NI'm floating above a deep valley.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.21,0:19:08.14,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Balsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:08.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm falling! I'm falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.21,0:19:09.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm falling! I'm falling!\NDon't let Chagum drag you across!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.95,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's being pulled into Nayug!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:13.12,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:16.08,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be the anchor\Nthat keeps Chagum fixed in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.08,0:19:17.49,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:22.26,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Chagum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.79,0:19:27.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The valley that you're seeing\Ndoesn't exist here in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:31.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What you're seeing is\Nthe landscape of Nayug.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.07,0:19:33.37,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:38.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your body is still right here in Sag...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:42.54,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be fine.\NYou aren't going to fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.95,0:19:48.25,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum, I want you\Nto calm yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.25,0:19:50.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and focus on\NBalsa's arms around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.72,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Do you feel them now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:57.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Use Balsa's body as your guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:01.80,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Moving outwards from where she's\Ntouching you, sense your own body.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.96,0:20:05.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slowly bring your mind\Nback to this side.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.23,0:20:08.20,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what it looks like here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:11.97,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're at Hunter's Hole,\Nthe place you've been living all winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.81,0:20:18.51,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see me, Chagum?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.86,0:20:28.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.86,0:20:30.96,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chagum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:39.43,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. His soul has\Nreturned to this world. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.24,0:20:44.01,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this happened\Nbecause of the egg?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.37,0:20:46.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it is almost spring...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:52.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this means\Nit's finally started.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:08.40,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is the work progressing,\NMaster Gakai?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:14.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm amazed. To think that so many\Nepitaphs were hidden beneath our feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:23.55,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot help but feel regret\Nat all the time we have wasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.65,0:21:25.91,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How are preparations\Ngoing on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.35,0:21:29.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was finally able to determine\Nthe approximate location...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.35,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...of the land of feasting\Nthe other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.15,0:21:33.32,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.69,0:21:36.16,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,However, recovering\Nthe very last of the tablets...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:39.90,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...from the lowest, flooded levels\Nis taking much time and effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.33,0:21:44.10,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, many of\Nthem contain information...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.10,0:21:46.07,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that is crucial to\Nour understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.20,0:21:50.87,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Though I would prefer to obtain all\Navailable information as soon as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:53.04,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I ask that you rest a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:56.65,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you should direct\Nthose words at yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.65,0:21:59.28,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have dark circles\Nunder your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.78,0:22:04.59,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we have learned the\Nsecret behind the country's founding...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.59,0:22:07.09,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...we cannot afford to\Nhave you collapse on us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:11.19,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this to us. Mark my\Nwords. We will finish in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.69,0:22:12.83,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Gakai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.63,0:22:14.73,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.66,0:22:17.93,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If we turn up anything,\Nwe will notify you at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.38,0:22:35.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master Shuga, the\Nmikado wishes to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.59,0:22:46.23,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When did we last have snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.63,0:22:50.03,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was about the time of the first\Nmonth of the new year, as I recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.37,0:22:52.50,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who would ever have\Nimagined that clear blue skies...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.50,0:22:56.84,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...would instill such dread and\Nfill my heart with such worry?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.72,0:23:13.05,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I sat huddled and alone, holding\Nback the tears on those nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.05,0:23:20.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When it felt like I was about\Nto succumb to my doubts...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.20,0:23:25.47,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...there you were,\Nat my side before I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.47,0:23:32.81,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was none other than you\Nwho was there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.81,0:23:47.09,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I keep wishing, "I want to be strong."\NI stumble and hurt myself again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.09,0:23:56.46,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But because I have you to believe in,\NI can get back to my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:24:03.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I simply want to tell\Nmy dear one, "Thank you. "
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.24,0:24:08.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,At the top of my lungs,\Nagain and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.38,0:24:16.75,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I call out to my precious loved one.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.75,0:24:20.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is my voice reaching you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:29.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In this world that always changes,\Nhuman warmth never does.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.20,0:24:39.51,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain I sensed the presence\Nof the one that I hold dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:45.20,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.04,0:24:45.21,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The egg awakens\Nwith the spring thaw...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.51,0:24:48.68,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...and the being from another world\Nalso reaches its time of emergence.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.52,0:24:52.02,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time,\N"In Search of the Shigu Salua."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.02,0:24:57.03,Signs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 23\NIn Search of the Shigu Salua
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.85,0:24:56.36,Dialogue,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The scent of flowers draws everyone\Nto the last place they can be found.
